OL,3,C'Dangerous' motorcyclist banned after
OL,4,Cpolice set up operation to arrest him
OL,6,FVideo footage of a "dangerous"
OL,7,Fmotorcyclist has been released after
OL,8,Fpolice set up an operation to catch
OL,9,Fhim after he was seen riding at
OL,10,F"grossly excessive" speeds on several
OL,11,Foccasions.
OL,13,FKieran Jones, from, was recorded on a
OL,14,Fspeed camera on the A22 Eastbourne
OL,15,FRoad in Halland, , travelling as fast
OL,16,Fas 80mph in a 30mph zone on seven
OL,17,Foccasions but had concealed his number
OL,18,Fplate to avoid detection.
