OL,3,C'Dangerous' motorcyclist banned after
OL,4,Cpolice set up operation to arrest him
OL,6,FHe appeared at Crawley Magistrates'
OL,7,Fcourt on 11 March where he admitted
OL,8,Fdangerous driving, driving without due
OL,9,Fcare and attention, failing to stop,
OL,10,Ffailing to comply with a solid white
OL,11,Fline road marking, and eight counts of
OL,12,Fspeeding between July last year and
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,FJones was disqualified from driving
OL,16,Ffor three years and ordered to
OL,17,Fcomplete 225 hours of unpaid work as
OL,18,Fpart of a six-month suspended prison
OL,19,Fsentence.
