OL,6,FHe was also ordered to complete 18
OL,7,Frehabilitation activity requirement
OL,8,F(RAR) sessions, with #85 costs and a
OL,9,F#154 surcharge.
OL,11,FSergeant Peter Swash from Sussex
OL,12,FPolice's roads policing unit said:
OL,13,F"Jones's riding was highly reckless,
OL,14,Ftravelling at grossly excessive speeds
OL,15,Fwhile concealing his registration
OL,16,Fplate in order to avoid detection.
