OL,6,F"Officers were determined to catch him
OL,7,Fbecause of the risks he posed to other
OL,8,Froads users and of course to himself,
OL,9,Fso we set up an operation and were
OL,10,Fable to safely pursue and stop him.
OL,12,F"We are pleased that a dangerous rider
OL,13,Fhas been taken off our roads."
OL,15,FA force spokesman said: "Speeding is
OL,16,Fone of the main reasons why people are
OL,17,Fkilled or seriously injured on our
OL,18,Froads.
